---------------------------------------------------------------------
For "Pinatubo"-simulation (diagnostic !) set in xmessy_mmd:

   NML_TIMER[1]=timer_T42L90MA.nml
   NML_IMPORT[1]=import_s199101.nml
   NML_RAD[1]=rad_test.nml
   NML_AEROPT[1]=aeropt_test.nml

---------------------------------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------------------------------
OBSOLETE In order to use old rad4all:
OBSOLETE ============================
OBSOLETE 
OBSOLETE 1) switch on RAD4ALL in switch.nml
OBSOLETE 
OBSOLETE 2) either: switch off RAD in switch.nml (and also CLOUDOPT, AEROPT)
OBSOLETE    or    : switch off l_feedback in rad.nml
OBSOLETE 
OBSOLETE 3) set NML_ORBIT[1]=orbit_rad4all.nml in xmessy_mmd
